== Chart performance ==
Upon the release of the album, "Glassheart" debut at number 27 on the [[UK Dance Chart]] on 21 October 2012.<ref name="UKDanceDebut27">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/18/2012-10-27/|title=2012 Top 40 Dance Singles Archive 27th October 2012|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|date=21 October 2012|accessdate=21 October 2012}}</ref> It also debuted at number 167 on the [[UK Singles Chart]].<ref name="UKSinglesDebut">{{cite web|url=http://zobbel.de/cluk/121027cluk.txt|title=Chart: CL UK Update|work=zobbel.de|publisher=Official Charts Company|date=27 October 2012|accessdate=22 November 2012}}</ref>

